###
### Payment Gateway API Tests
### Base URL: https://localhost:7092//api/payments
###

### ============================================================================
### POST /api/payments - Create Payments
### ============================================================================

### 1. Authorized Payment (Card ending in 1234) odd number
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments
Idempotency-Key: {{guid_authorized}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardNumber": "12345678901234",
  "expiryMonth": 12,
  "expiryYear": 2028,
  "currency": "GBP",
  "amount": 1000,
  "cvv": "123"
}

###

### 2. Declined Payment (Card ending in 2345) - even number
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments
Idempotency-Key: {{guid_declined}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardNumber": "123456789012345",
  "expiryMonth": 6,
  "expiryYear": 2028,
  "currency": "GBP",
  "amount": 5000,
  "cvv": "456"
}

###

### 3. Rejected Payment (Invalid - Missing CVV) - Rejected due to missing CVV
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments
Idempotency-Key: {{guid_rejected}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardNumber": "1234567890123456",
  "expiryMonth": 3,
  "expiryYear": 2027,
  "currency": "USD",
  "amount": 2000,
  "cvv": "45"
}

###

### 4. Idempotency Test - Same request should return same payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments
Idempotency-Key: {{guid_authorized}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardNumber": "4242424242424242",
  "expiryMonth": 12,
  "expiryYear": 2025,
  "currency": "GBP",
  "amount": 1000,
  "cvv": "123"
}

### ============================================================================
### GET /api/payments/{id} - Retrieve Payments
### ============================================================================
### Note: Replace {{paymentId}} with actual IDs returned from POST requests above

### 5. Retrieve Payment
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/{{paymentId}}

###

### ============================================================================
### Variables
### ============================================================================
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7092/
@guid_authorized = 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
@guid_declined = 22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222
@guid_rejected = 33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333
@paymentId = <replace-with-actual-id-from-response>
